ds, tell them, &quot;Ok, 100 plat, and I'll consider it&quot;.  People from other guilds who deserve(The Nameless has some pretty decent uberguilds compared to other servers) a bit better treatment will generally not deserve the &quot;asshole treatment&quot;, but may also not deserve the port if you arn't in the mood, but always tell them, &quot;Sorry, I'm not porting right now&quot;.  The ones who don't show YOU any respect, just ignore them. <br>
